  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/digitalcamera/\" rel=\"tag\">数码相机</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/10/07/samsung-nx300M-360-degree-rotatable-display/\"><img src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/10/samsung-nx300m-2013-10-07-02.jpg\" style=\"margin: 4px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n三星之前的 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/01/04/samsung-nx300-mirrorless-camera-3D/\">NX300</a> 无反相机除了 3D 噱头之外似乎并没有太多卖点，而现在他们又推出了型号为 NX300M 的升级款，它新增了一块可翻转 180 度的 3.31 吋 AMOLED 触控屏幕，让消费者多了一个选择它的理由。除此之外规格基本上都维持了原样，2,030 万像素 APS-C 感光元件、100 至 25,600 ISO 范围、8.6fps JPG 连拍模式、双频 Wi-Fi、SmartShare、NFC 等均得到保留。据悉这款产品目前已在韩国开卖，有黑、白、褐三种配色，搭配 18-55mm Kit 镜的价格为 890,000 韩元（约人民币 5,120 元）。<br />\n<div class=\"postgallery\"><p><strong>Gallery: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/samsung-nx300m-press-shots/\">Samsung NX300M Press Shots</a></strong></p><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/samsung-nx300m-press-shots/6222787/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/10/nx300m-004-dynamic-white-2013-10-07-1_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/samsung-nx300m-press-shots/6222788/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/10/nx300m-006-front-white-2013-10-07-1_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/samsung-nx300m-press-shots/6222789/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/10/nx300m-012-dynamic-white-2013-10-07-1_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/samsung-nx300m-press-shots/6222790/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/10/nx300m-16mm-001-front-black-2013-10-07-1_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/samsung-nx300m-press-shots/6222791/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/10/nx300m-16mm-001-front-brown-2013-